extendedInfo.description: Addictive puzzle game. Figure out a way to guide the block through obstacles and let it slide into exit. Use switches to toggle bridges. After several easy levels real fun begins, where reaching the exit won't be as easy anymore. All levels solvable !v1.1.2 High resolution support.v1.1.6 Tablets support.Keywords: amtal, amtale, box, blox, block, cube, roll, puzzle, logic.
